        "description": {
            "chat": "",
            "unidentified": "",
            "value": "<p>Viciously sharp spiked chains wrap around this @Compendium[pf2e.equipment-srd.Studded Leather Armor]{Studded Leather Armor}that can be used to magically harm the wearer and channel supernatural abilities without somehow tearing at the leather itself.<br /><br />The<em>barbed vest</em>doesn't fuse to you in the usual way. It can be removed and discarded, but 1 day after doing so, you feel driven to recollect the vest at any cost until the curse is removed with a @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Remove Curse]{Remove Curse}spell.<br /><br />Anytime you activate the<em>barbed vest</em>, its chains tighten around you, dealing<a class=\"inline-roll roll\" title=\"persistent piercing damage\" data-mode=\"roll\" data-flavor=\"persistent piercing damage\" data-formula=\"1d6\"> 1d6</a>persistent piercing damage. You can remove this persistent damage as normal, but only after deactivating the item's magic as a single action.<br /><br /><strong>Activate</strong><span style=\"font-family: 'Pathfinder2eActions'; font-size: 1.8em; display: inline;\">2</span>Interact;</p>\n<p><strong>Frequency</strong>once per day;</p>\n<p><strong>Effect</strong>The<em>barbed vest</em>casts @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Spiritual Weapon]{Spiritual Weapon}, summoning a @Compendium[pf2e.equipment-srd.Spiked Chain]{Spiked Chain}to fight for you.</p>"
